co.cask.cdap.api.flow.flowlet
Interface OutputEmitter<T>

Type Parameters:
T - Type of data that could be emitted by this OutputEmitter.
public interface OutputEmitter<T>

This interface defines an emitter used for emitting events from within a flowlet.
